prodNameC: 亞培設計師巨細胞病毒IgG抗體檢驗試劑組
ingredientsDesc:
ARCHITECT CMV IgG Reagent Kit, 100 / 400 Tests
Microparticles：1 or 4 Bottle(s) (6.6 mL per 100-test bottle) 
CMV virus lysate coated microparticles in TRIS buffered saline. Minimum concentration：0.08% solids.
Conjugate：1 or 4 Bottle(s) (5.9 mL per 100-test bottle) Murine 
acridinium-labeled anti-human IgG in MES buffer. Minimum concentration：44 ng/mL.
Assay Diluent：1 or 4 Bottle(s) (10.0 mL per 100-test bottle) 
CMV IgG assay diluent containing calf serum and MES buffer.

ARCHITECT CMV IgG Controls
3 Bottles (8.0 mL each) of ARCHITECT CMV IgG Controls：Negative Control, Positive Control 1 and Positive Control 2 containing recalcified human plasma.
                            Target Anti-
                            Cytomegalovirus       Control Range 
                            IgG Concentration
Control          Color          (AU/mL)                  (AU/mL)
CONTROL-    Natural          N/A                        <=3.1
CONTROL1+ Natural          30.0                     15.0-45.0
CONTROL2+ Natural        150.0                   75.0-225.0

ARCHITECT CMV IgG Calibrators
6 Bottle (4.0 mL each) of ARCHITECT CMV IgG calibrators containing recalcified human plasma.
Calibrator    Target Anti-Cytomegalovirus IgG 
                  Concentration (AU/mL)
CAL A         0
CAL B         10.0
CAL C         50.0
CAL D         75.0
CAL E         125.0
CAL F         250.0
